---
// layout
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
	tabTitle="About"
	description="Learn more about Avinash, a frontend developer who loves building things for the web and diving into technical rabbit holes."
>
	<section class="intro">
		<h1>A bit about me</h1>
		<div class="intro-content">
			<p>
				I disappear into web rabbit holes, moving from technical docs to
				business case studies. I'm constantly curious about why certain
				things work, what pain points are being solved, and how we can
				use the web to build something meaningful.
			</p>

			<p>
				Big fan of technology and open source software. I'm still
				figuring out myself, evolving big time, and honestly enjoying
				the journey.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2 class="section-title">Lately</h2>
		<div class="lately-content">
			<p>
				Shipping small, focused projects to sharpen the craft. Exploring
				patterns that make things scale without the overhead. Always
				learning something new.
			</p>
			<div class="next-up">
				<span class="label">Next on my list:</span>
				<code class="stack">Bun + Hono + Cloudflare</code>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2 class="section-title">Random bits</h2>
		<div class="bits-grid">
			<div class="bit-card">
				<p>Prefers chai over coffee (green tea is overrated)</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bit-card">
				<p>Team Android, always</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bit-card">
				<p>Main colors: black, white, blue, and gray</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bit-card">
				<p>
					Types at <a
						target="_blank"
						href="https://monkeytype.com/profile/Avi-Lvs">70wpm</a
					>
					<small>(best: 83wpm)</small>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bit-card wide">
				<p>Advocate for 'shipping' over 'polishing forever'</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2 class="section-title">Other</h2>
		<p class="other-links">
			Public notes <a href="/notes">here</a>. Books I've read + thoughts <a
				href="/books">here</a
			>
		</p>
	</section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
	.intro {
		margin-bottom: 5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.intro-content {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 65ch;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.about-section {
		margin-bottom: 5rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		display: block;
	}

	.lately-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.lately-content p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.next-up {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.next-up .label {
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.stack {
		background: var(--accent-bg);
		color: var(--accent);
		padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.bits-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.bit-card {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--bg-soft);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		transition: var(--transition);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.bit-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent);
		background: var(--bg);
	}

	.bit-card p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.bit-card.wide {
		grid-column: span 2;
	}

	.other-links {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.intro {
			margin-bottom: 4rem;
		}

		.bit-card.wide {
			grid-column: span 1;
		}

		.bits-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.about-section {
			margin-bottom: 4rem;
		}
	}
</style>
